'''人民運營商'''（{{lang-en|The People's Operator}}，[[縮寫|縮寫]]'''TPO'''）是一間[[移动虚拟运营商|移动虚拟运营商]]，分別在[[英國|英國]]和[[美國|美國]]透過[[EE_(電信公司)|EE]]以及[[Sprint|史普林特公司]]提供行動電話服務。該公司在上市第一年到2016年間股價下跌了近90%。<ref name="thetimesJun16">{{cite news|url=http://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/investors-hang-up-on-wikipedia-founder-rz9w2xdc9|title=Investors hang up on Wikipedia founder|publisher=[[泰晤士报|泰晤士报]]|first=Nic|last=Fildes|date=2016-06-15|access-date=2016-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701210911/http://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/investors-hang-up-on-wikipedia-founder-rz9w2xdc9|archive-date=2016-07-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 歷史 ==
人民營運商成立於2012年11月19日，由三名創始人{{link-en|安德魯·羅森菲爾德|Andrew Rosenfeld}}、湯姆·古特里奇和馬克·艾普斯坦共同擁有。<ref name="ibtimesNov12">{{cite news |title=Ethical Mobile Phone Network The People's Operator Launches |url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/articles/406342/20121119/people-s-operator-launches-25-profits-charity.htm |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131026153737/http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/articles/406342/20121119/people-s-operator-launches-25-profits-charity.htm |archivedate=2013-10-26 |accessdate=2016-08-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>其總部位在[[倫敦|倫敦]][[肖迪奇|肖迪奇]]，羅森菲爾德為主席，艾普斯坦為副主席，[[首席执行官|執行長]]則由艾力克斯·法蘭克斯擔任。<ref name="digitalspyNov12"><cite class="citation news">[http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tech/news/a439153/the-peoples-operator-launches-as-charitable-mobile-network.html "The People's Operator launches as charitable mobile network"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tech/news/a439153/the-peoples-operator-launches-as-charitable-mobile-network.html |date=20151007071557 }}. </cite></ref><ref name="huffingtonNov12"><cite class="citation news">[http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2012/11/19/charitable-mobile-network-tpo-the-peoples-operator_n_2157356.html "Charitable Mobile Network TPO Pitches Itself As 'The People's Operator'"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2012/11/19/charitable-mobile-network-tpo-the-peoples-operator_n_2157356.html |date=20160304060330 }}. </cite></ref>

2014年1月20日，TPO宣布维基百科的创始人[[吉米·威爾斯|吉米·威爾斯]]領取250,000英镑的年薪加入此組織，<ref>[https://www.thepeoplesoperator.com/files/public/The%20People's%20Operator%20plc%20-%20AIM%20Admission%20Document.pdf AIM Admission document] {{Wayback|url=https://www.thepeoplesoperator.com/files/public/The%20People%27s%20Operator%20plc%20-%20AIM%20Admission%20Document.pdf |date=20160311225654 }}; The People’s Operator plc (incorporated and registered in England and Wales with registered no. 09083874) Placing of 15,384,616 Ordinary Shares at 130 pence per share and Admission of Enlarged Share Capital to trading on AIM; 28 November 2014</ref>作為董事會聯合主席，并決定「采取战略性的商業手法」，威尔士認為：「TPO具有巨大的潜在增长，將會需要更多的钱來滿足人民和社区的需要。」<ref name="mobilJan14"><cite class="citation news">Carol Millett (20 January 2014). </cite></ref><ref name="telegraphJan14"><cite class="citation news">[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/jimmy-wales/10583554/Wikipedia-founder-Jimmy-Wales-backs-viral-mobile-network-The-Peoples-Operator.html "Wikipedia founder Jimmy Wales backs 'viral mobile network' The People's Operator"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/jimmy-wales/10583554/Wikipedia-founder-Jimmy-Wales-backs-viral-mobile-network-The-Peoples-Operator.html |date=20160704184043 }}. </cite></ref>

TPO在2014年一月宣布，在未来的12个月，它將進入更廣泛的[[美国|美国]]和[[欧洲|欧洲]]市場。<ref name="mobilJan14"><cite class="citation news">Carol Millett (20 January 2014). </cite></ref><ref name="nextwebJan14"><cite class="citation news">[http://thenextweb.com/insider/2014/01/20/jimmy-wales-joins-uks-growth-global-community/ "Jimmy Wales takes his Wikipedia learnings to the mobile industry as Co-Chair of The People’s Operator"] {{Wayback|url=http://thenextweb.com/insider/2014/01/20/jimmy-wales-joins-uks-growth-global-community/ |date=20161128101711 }}. </cite></ref> 在2014年十月，该公司宣布它打算在伦敦的[[另类投资市场|另类投资市场]]上市。據奥斯卡·威廉-格拉特預估，该公司股票會由100萬英鎊起跳。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.standard.co.uk/business/business-news/wikipedia-founder-backs-peoples-operator-plans-aim-listing-9791021.html|title=Wikipedia founder backs People's Operator plans AIM listing|accessdate=2014-10-16|author=Williams-Grut, Oscar|date=2014-10-13|work=Evening Standard|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141015141047/http://www.standard.co.uk/business/business-news/wikipedia-founder-backs-peoples-operator-plans-aim-listing-9791021.html|archive-date=2014-10-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>

TPO于2015年七月21日在美國開始發展<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/wikipedia-founder-jimmy-wales-launching-social-network-phone-service-2015-7|title=Wikipedia founder Jimmy Wales is launching a social network and phone service to make it easier to donate to charity|accessdate=2015-07-22|author=Tweedie, Steven|date=2015-07-21|work=Business Insider|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150722182833/http://www.businessinsider.com/wikipedia-founder-jimmy-wales-launching-social-network-phone-service-2015-7|archive-date=2015-07-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="fast_Jimm">{{Cite news|url=http://www.fastcompany.com/3048510/jimmy-wales-wants-you-to-feel-good-about-paying-your-cell-phone-bill|title=Jimmy Wales Wants You To Feel Good About Paying Your Cell Phone Bill|last=Titlow|first=John Paul|date=2015-07-21|work=Fast Company|accessdate=2015-08-13|quote=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150813051101/http://www.fastcompany.com/3048510/jimmy-wales-wants-you-to-feel-good-about-paying-your-cell-phone-bill|archive-date=2015-08-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>，採用[[Sprint|史普林特]]提供T-Mobile US和GSM网络服務。2016年3月21日起，它採取了新方案，客户月繳32美元即可具有无限的通话时间和2000兆字節的文字数据保存。<ref name="reco_Wiki">{{Cite news|url=http://recode.net/2015/07/21/wikipedia-founder-jimmy-wales-brings-charity-mobile-network-to-u-s/|title=Wikipedia Founder Jimmy Wales Brings Charity Mobile Network to U.S.|last=Fried|first=Ina|date=2015-07-21|work=Re/code|accessdate=2015-08-13|quote=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150813203144/http://recode.net/2015/07/21/wikipedia-founder-jimmy-wales-brings-charity-mobile-network-to-u-s/|archive-date=2015-08-13|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="then_Wiki">{{Cite news|url=http://thenextweb.com/insider/2015/07/21/wikipedia-founder-launches-the-peoples-operator-ad-free-social-network-for-social-good/|title=Wikipedia founder launches The People's Operator ad-free social network for social good|last=Connolly|first=Amanda|date=2015-07-21|work=The Next Web|accessdate=2015-08-13|quote=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150813203148/http://thenextweb.com/insider/2015/07/21/wikipedia-founder-launches-the-peoples-operator-ad-free-social-network-for-social-good/|archive-date=2015-08-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年九月，该公司發表了财务報告，2015年的前半年總共虧損了4,400,000英鎊，比起去年一整年僅虧損600,000英鎊還多了幾倍有餘。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.iii.co.uk/stockmarketwire/268888/tpops-loss?context=LSE:TPOP|title=TPOP's loss|accessdate=2015-10-26|date=2015-09-29|work=Interactive Investor; StockMarketWire|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151006044234/http://www.iii.co.uk/stockmarketwire/268888/tpops-loss?context=LSE:TPOP|archive-date=2015-10-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年10月到2016年三月，该公司股價大崩潰，認售權證從原本的130張降到低于30張。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.google.co.uk/finance/historical?cid=1049505660391846&startdate=Oct+1%2C+2014&enddate=Apr+1%2C+2016&num=30|title=The People's Operator PLC (LON:TPOP) – historical prices|publisher=[[Google_Finance|Google Finance]]|access-date=2016-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160426005202/https://www.google.co.uk/finance/historical?cid=1049505660391846&startdate=Oct+1%2C+2014&enddate=Apr+1%2C+2016&num=30|archive-date=2016-04-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[泰晤士报|泰晤士報]]在2016年6月的報導指出，它的股價比上市時下降了約90%。<ref name="thetimesJun16"/>

== 服务 ==
作为一个[[移动虚拟运营商|移动虚拟运营商]]，TPO不拥有任何网络基础设施，而是使用[[EE_(電信公司)|EE]]在英國提供其服务<ref name="ibtimesNov12"/>（但一開始沒有承認），<ref name="bbcNov12"><cite class="citation news">[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-20394691 "Charitable mobile network The People's Operator launches"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-20394691 |date=20160721234026 }}. </cite></ref>並在美国使用[[Sprint|史普林特]]网络。它經由[[Transatel|Transatel]]连接到EE网络。<ref name="huffingtonNov12"><cite class="citation news">[http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2012/11/19/charitable-mobile-network-tpo-the-peoples-operator_n_2157356.html "Charitable Mobile Network TPO Pitches Itself As 'The People's Operator'"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2012/11/19/charitable-mobile-network-tpo-the-peoples-operator_n_2157356.html |date=20160304060330 }}. </cite></ref>

TPO有提供預付手機的服务。<ref name="ibtimesNov12"/>该组织没有线上存储、运行的功能，但是它有[[呼叫中心|呼叫中心]]。<ref name="lintNov12"><cite class="citation news">[http://www.pocket-lint.com/news/118167-mobile-network-peoples-operator-launched "New UK mobile network The People's Operator aims to be ethical"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.pocket-lint.com/news/118167-mobile-network-peoples-operator-launched |date=20160809084825 }}. </cite></ref>2016年，TPO宣布它将拋棄EE，改使用{{Internal link helper/en|Three UK|Three UK}}的网络，这将讓其客户可享受LTE 4G的服务。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thepeoplesoperator.com/view-post/15150/press-releases|title=The People’s Operator partners with Three UK and targets 4G launch|date=2005-11-03|publisher=The People’s Operator|access-date=2015-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117023040/https://www.thepeoplesoperator.com/view-post/15150/press-releases|archive-date=2015-11-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

== TPO基金會 ==
TPO利潤的25％用於TPO基金會，這是英國的一個獨立慈善機構和社區團體。此外，TPO客戶可以選擇將其電話費的10％捐出。<ref name="ibtimesNov12"/>这10％来自TPO的营销预算。<ref name="telegraphJan14"><cite class="citation news">[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/jimmy-wales/10583554/Wikipedia-founder-Jimmy-Wales-backs-viral-mobile-network-The-Peoples-Operator.html "Wikipedia founder Jimmy Wales backs 'viral mobile network' The People's Operator"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/jimmy-wales/10583554/Wikipedia-founder-Jimmy-Wales-backs-viral-mobile-network-The-Peoples-Operator.html |date=20160704184043 }}. </cite></ref>2013年9月，[[工党_(英国)|英國工黨]]宣布將和TPO合作。根據《{{Internal link helper/en|Wired UK|Wired UK}}》的說法，工黨鼓勵其黨員多繳10%的黨費，工黨收到後再將那些錢轉交給TPO基金會。<ref name="WiredLabour">{{Cite web|url=http://www.wired.co.uk/news/archive/2014-01/20/jimmy-wales-tpo|title=Jimmy Wales joins mobile network The People's Operator|author=Olivia Solon|date=2014-01-20|work=Wired|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140122074456/http://www.wired.co.uk/news/archive/2014-01/20/jimmy-wales-tpo|archivedate=2014-01-22|accessdate=2015-10-28}}</ref>

2014年一月威尔士加入TPO後，该基金会亦捐款支持[[维基百科|维基百科]]。<ref name="telegraphJan14"><cite class="citation news">[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/jimmy-wales/10583554/Wikipedia-founder-Jimmy-Wales-backs-viral-mobile-network-The-Peoples-Operator.html "Wikipedia founder Jimmy Wales backs 'viral mobile network' The People's Operator"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/jimmy-wales/10583554/Wikipedia-founder-Jimmy-Wales-backs-viral-mobile-network-The-Peoples-Operator.html |date=20160704184043 }}. </cite></ref>

